item.title: CVE-2023-2529|2024-08-02T06:26:09.726Z -- unknown -- enable%20svg%20uploads
item.description: The Enable SVG Uploads WordPress plugin through 2.1.5 does not sanitise uploaded SVG files, which could allow users with a role as low as Author to upload a malicious SVG containing XSS payloads.
